name: Food Rush (Zoey-21)
description:
As the 10,000 customer to the shop you get free groceries for a limited time! Grab as much as you can!

Part of the Mini Jam 88: Rush with the limitation of "Tell a story with no text"

For every foodstuff you get to the cashier you get 3 seconds.

If you bring a foodstuff that is on the bottom of the screen you get 6 seconds.

Source Code: https://github.com/Zoey-21/food-rush
